<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT68">
<l>tiṟampēṉmiṉ kaṇṭīr tiruvaṭitaṉ nāma</l>
<l>maṟantum puṟantoḻā mānta riṟaiñciyuñ</l>
<l>cātuvarāyp pōtumiṉka ḷeṉṟāṉ namaṉumtaṉ</l>
<l>tūtuvaraik kūvic cevikku.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>‘Look, do not swerve [from this]: leave like good people,</l>
<l>bowing down to the human beings who</l>
<l>do not worship a foreign [god] even if they forget God,’ said Yama</l>
<l>In the ears of [his] messengers, summoning [them].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
